drop table if exists gedmo_media;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: gedmo_media */
/*==============================================================*/
create table gedmo_media
(
id int(11) not null auto_increment,
category int(11) default NULL,
media int(11) default NULL,
status varchar(255) not null,
title varchar(255) default NULL,
url varchar(314) default NULL,
mediaId int(11) default NULL,
mediadelete tinyint(1) default NULL,
created_at datetime not null,
updated_at datetime default NULL,
published_at date default NULL,
archive_at datetime default NULL,
enabled tinyint(1) default NULL,
position int(11) default NULL,
primary key (id),
key IDX_43EF489E64C19C1 (category),
key IDX_43EF489E6A2CA10C (media)
);

alter table gedmo_media add constraint FK_43EF489E64C19C1 foreign key (category)
references gedmo_category (id);
